---
/**
 * Landing Page — Single-page showcase
 * Clean, verified, zero broken links.
 * Full site coming soon.
 */
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Naveen Riaz | நவீன் ரியாஸ்</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Every organisation is alive. Nurture its Mind, Body & Soul. Watch it thrive."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logo.svg" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- ═══ Hero ═══ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-symbol" aria-hidden="true">ஃ</div>
        <h1 class="animate-in">Naveen Riaz</h1>
        <p class="hero-tamil animate-in animate-delay-1">நவீன் ரியாஸ் மொஹமத் கனி</p>
        <p class="hero-tagline animate-in animate-delay-2">
          Every organisation is alive.<br />
          Nurture its <span class="c-mind">Mind</span>,
          <span class="c-body">Body</span> &amp;
          <span class="c-soul">Soul</span>.<br />
          Watch it thrive.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ═══ Dimensions ═══ -->
    <section class="dimensions">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="dim-grid">
          <div class="dim-card dim-card--mind animate-in animate-delay-1">
            <div class="dim-dot" style="background: var(--mind-color);"></div>
            <h3>Think</h3>
            <p class="dim-tamil">சிந்தனை (Sinthanai)</p>
            <p>Frameworks for structured reasoning. SPAR deliberation protocol. STEAL intelligence capture. A cognitive architecture for the AI era.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dim-card dim-card--body animate-in animate-delay-2">
            <div class="dim-dot" style="background: var(--body-color);"></div>
            <h3>Work</h3>
            <p class="dim-tamil">செயல் (Seyal)</p>
            <p>Proof of work across three layers. What I aspire to build (Soul). What my mind is cooking (Mind). What has shipped (Body).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="dim-card dim-card--soul animate-in animate-delay-3">
            <div class="dim-dot" style="background: var(--soul-color);"></div>
            <h3>Play</h3>
            <p class="dim-tamil">ஆன்மா (Aanma)</p>
            <p>Tamil roots, philosophical detours, origin stories. The fire underneath everything. Identity: Calling, Origin, Reason, Endurance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ Kural ═══ -->
    <section class="kural-section">
      <div class="container container--narrow">
        <blockquote class="kural">
          <p class="kural-tamil">
            தொட்டனைத் தூறும் மணற்கேணி மாந்தர்க்குக்<br />
            கற்றனைத் தூறும் அறிவு.
          </p>
          <p class="kural-en">Like a well that springs as you dig, knowledge springs as you learn.</p>
          <cite>Thirukkural #396</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ What I'm Building ═══ -->
    <section class="building">
      <div class="container container--narrow">
        <h2>What I'm <span class="gt">Building</span></h2>

        <div class="build-list">
          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--live">Live</span>
            <div>
              <strong>SPAR-Kit</strong> — Open source CLI for structured multi-persona deliberation.
              <a href="https://github.com/synthanai/spar-kit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--live">Live</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Intent of Thought</strong> — GPS for AI reasoning. Published on arXiv.
              <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.02896" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Paper →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--live">Live</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Neural Canvas</strong> — 20 articles across five series on living organisations, AI, and pattern connections.
              <a href="https://mnaveenriaz.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Blog →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--cooking">Cooking</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Let's SPAR</strong> — My first book. 33 chapters on structured dialectic thinking. Publication-ready.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--cooking">Cooking</span>
            <div>
              <strong>SYNTHAI Ecosystem</strong> — 24 repositories, 19 knowledge items, 1000+ commits. A living organisation operating system.
              <a href="https://github.com/synthanai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub →</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="build-item">
            <span class="build-status build-status--cooking">Cooking</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Thirukkural Mapping</strong> — Bridging 2000-year-old Tamil wisdom to modern leadership. VOW Book 1 in active writing.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ Collision ═══ -->
    <section class="collision-section">
      <div class="container container--narrow">
        <h2>Collisions</h2>
        <p class="collision-desc">
          A <strong>Collision</strong> is an intellectual event, not a blog post.
          Two ideas from different domains crash into each other and produce a new pattern.
          If there is no crash, it is not a collision.
        </p>
        <div class="collision-list">
          <a class="collision-item" href="https://mnaveenriaz.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="collision-title">The $1 Notebook</span>
            <span class="collision-sub">Handwriting × SPAR × Purpose Amnesia → PENA synthesis</span>
          </a>
          <a class="collision-item" href="https://mnaveenriaz.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="collision-title">Architecture Is the Moat</span>
            <span class="collision-sub">Three practitioners, three domains, one conclusion: your AI model doesn't matter</span>
          </a>
          <a class="collision-item" href="https://mnaveenriaz.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <span class="collision-title">The Three Fatigues</span>
            <span class="collision-sub">AI Fatigue × Decision Fatigue × Judgement Fatigue (MBS spiral)</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ Connect ═══ -->
    <section class="connect">
      <div class="container container--narrow" style="text-align: center;">
        <h2>Vibe</h2>
        <p class="dim-tamil" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);">ஒலுக்கம் (Olukkam) — Resonance</p>
        <p>Every engagement starts the same way: a conversation.</p>
        <div class="connect-links">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mnaveenriaz/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/synthanai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://mnaveenriaz.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">Blog</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ Footer ═══ -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
        <p class="footer-symbol">ஃ</p>
        <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 Naveen Riaz Mohamed Kani</p>
        <p class="footer-note">Built with Astro. Powered by the SYNTHAI ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <style>
      /* ── Hero ── */
      .hero {
        min-height: 80vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-xl);
      }

      .hero-inner {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .hero-symbol {
        font-family: var(--font-tamil);
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: var(--soul-color);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
        opacity: 0.6;
        animation: pulseGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
      }

      .hero-tamil {
        font-family: var(--font-tamil);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--tamil-accent);
        opacity: 0.7;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
      }

      .hero-tagline {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .c-mind { color: var(--mind-color); font-weight: 600; }
      .c-body { color: var(--body-color); font-weight: 600; }
      .c-soul { color: var(--soul-color); font-weight: 600; }
      .gt { color: var(--soul-color); }

      /* ── Dimensions ── */
      .dimensions {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      }

      .dim-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: var(--space-lg);
      }

      .dim-card {
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        padding: var(--space-xl);
        transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
      }

      .dim-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
      }

      .dim-card--mind { border-top: 3px solid var(--mind-color); }
      .dim-card--mind:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--mind-glow); }
      .dim-card--body { border-top: 3px solid var(--body-color); }
      .dim-card--body:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--body-glow); }
      .dim-card--soul { border-top: 3px solid var(--soul-color); }
      .dim-card--soul:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--soul-glow); }

      .dim-dot {
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px currentColor;
      }

      .dim-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
      }

      .dim-tamil {
        font-family: var(--font-tamil);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--tamil-accent);
        opacity: 0.7;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      }

      .dim-card p:last-child {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
      }

      /* ── Kural ── */
      .kural-section {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      }

      .kural {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0;
        padding: var(--space-xl);
        border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.12);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 168, 67, 0.03) 0%, transparent 100%);
      }

      .kural-tamil {
        font-family: var(--font-tamil);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--soul-color);
        line-height: 2;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
      }

      .kural-en {
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      }

      .kural cite {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--soul-color);
        opacity: 0.5;
        font-style: normal;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      }

      /* ── Building ── */
      .building {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      }

      .building h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
      }

      .build-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-md);
      }

      .build-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: var(--space-md);
        padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .build-status {
        font-family: var(--font-label);
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        padding: 3px 10px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        white-space: nowrap;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .build-status--live {
        color: var(--body-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--body-color);
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--body-glow);
      }

      .build-status--cooking {
        color: var(--mind-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--mind-color);
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--mind-glow);
      }

      /* ── Collisions ── */
      .collision-section {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      }

      .collision-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      }

      .collision-desc {
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
      }

      .collision-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-sm);
      }

      .collision-item {
        display: block;
        padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        border-left: 3px solid var(--soul-color);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
      }

      .collision-item:hover {
        transform: translateX(4px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--soul-glow);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .collision-title {
        display: block;
        font-family: var(--font-heading);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }

      .collision-sub {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      /* ── Connect ── */
      .connect {
        padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
      }

      .connect h2 {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
      }

      .connect-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: var(--space-md);
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      /* ── Footer ── */
      .footer {
        padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      }

      .footer-symbol {
        font-family: var(--font-tamil);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--soul-color);
        opacity: 0.4;
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      }

      .footer-copy {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
      }

      .footer-note {
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        color: var(--text-dim);
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
